-- Consultant Karl Motey Agrees to Plead Guilty in Insider Case, U.S. Says
-- B y   D a v i d   G l o v i n
-- 2010-12-23T20:30:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-23/consultant-karl-motey-agrees-to-plead-guilty-in-insider-case-u-s-says.html
Karl Motey, a consultant, agreed to
plead guilty and cooperate with investigators in a widening
insider-trading case, U.S. prosecutors said in a court filing
made public today. Motey will give details about tips received
from a source at Marvell Technology Group Ltd., according to the
filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Glovin in New York at 
 dglovin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Farr at 
 sfarr@bloomberg.net  